feat: establish OS model — every file maps to a kernel/driver/syscall/filesystem role

Archon Protocol is now explicitly framed as an operating system for AI agents:

- Kernel (always resident): AGENTS.md, archon.config.yaml, ai-index.md
- Drivers (loaded via skills: field): constraint skills = hard boundary enforcement
- System calls (user commands): init=boot, demand=exec, audit=stat, refactor=defrag, verifier=fsck
- Daemons (internal): self-auditor=watchdog, test-runner=testd
- Filesystem: docs/ with mount semantics (read-only, append-only, read-write)
- Installer: templates/install.sh, POST: tests/

